43:34.842 --> 43:39.113
Well, it was perfect timing.
I'm just sorry I wasn't here to greet you.

43:39.213 --> 43:42.782
That's all right. Trish has been lovely.

43:42.882 --> 43:45.219
And I've been getting a lot of artwork done.

43:45.319 --> 43:50.662
