that really... shook me up.

43:51.791 --> 43:53.461
Why, what happened?

43:53.561 --> 43:56.397
Well, I met this great-looking guy.

43:56.497 --> 43:58.666
And I used love magic on him.

43:58.966 --> 44:01.841
