Go home.

45:37.330 --> 45:39.654
Just ignore them.
They're always giving us trouble.

45:40.134 --> 45:42.770
I didn't know this town
was hostile to witches.

45:42.870 --> 45:47.141
Well, it's certainly not San Francisco.
But it's not bad for a small town.

45:47.641 --> 45:51.212
