teaching the staples...

46:31.719 --> 46:36.156
...energy grounding, earth-based
spirituality, pagan arts and crafts...

46:36.256 --> 46:40.828
...candle work, the spellcraft
master class, ancient mysticism...

46:40.928 --> 46:44.650
