47:03.283 --> 47:06.419
Yeah, some of us dance here
on amateur night. You should come.

47:09.022 --> 47:12.403
Hi, Barbara. Hi, Gahan. Sorry we're late.

47:13.293 --> 47:15.558
Hello, lovely ladies, please have a seat.

47:18.397 --> 47:22.002
Elaine, this is Star and her sister Moon.

47:22.102 --> 47:26.373
They're our students for tonight.
