47:52.665 --> 47:54.473
Then let us begin.

47:54.801 --> 47:58.672
All witches need to figure out
where their power lies.

47:58.772 --> 48:03.683
And we feel that a woman's
greatest power lies in her sexuality.

48:04.511 --> 48:09.183
We don't view this power
as satanic or anti-feminist...

48:09.283 --> 48:13.192
