48:43.316 --> 48:44.774
They teach us...

48:44.874 --> 48:48.862
...that a normative human being
is a hyper-rationalist, stoic male...

48:49.356 --> 48:52.173
...and that women's emotions
and intuitions...

48:52.273 --> 48:55.034
...are illnesses that need to be cured.

48:55.862 --> 48:59.376
And they believe that men
and women are different...

48:59.476 --> 49:03.242
...and that true equality
lies in that difference.

49:03.637 --> 49:06.025
We strive for male/female polarity...

49:06.125 --> 49:09.389
...and to regain our primal power
as goddesses.

49:10.077 --> 49:14.915
