49:21.521 --> 49:24.175
...learn to dress your hair
in attractive ways...

49:24.725 --> 49:29.301
...display flesh artfully,
and know what to conceal.

49:30.262 --> 49:32.393
Be a mother and a lover.

49:33.066 --> 49:34.976
Stand your ground...

49:35.076 --> 49:39.451
...but always let the man feel like a man.

49:39.972 --> 49:43.110
Use sex magic to destroy his fear of you...

49:43.210 --> 49:46.147
...and to open his heart
to the floodgates of love.

49:46.847 --> 49:50.550
Only then will he begin to see you
as a human being...

49:50.650 --> 49:52.659
...with all of your inner beauty.

49:53.087 --> 49:55.920
Then, when his heart is open to love...

49:56.020 --> 49:58.318
...you may do with him what you will.

50:19.212 --> 50:21.155
<i>I love you, Elaine.</i>

50:22.715 --> 50:24.757
<i>You know that, don't you?</i>

50:26.786 --> 50:28.827
