52:45.558 --> 52:48.057
Hast thou the courage to make the assay?

52:48.428 --> 52:53.505
I have two words,
perfect love and perfect trust.

53:11.383 --> 53:14.860
Assist me to erect the ancient altar...

53:15.621 --> 53:19.440
