53:19.859 --> 53:24.147
From the old times, a woman was the altar.

53:24.463 --> 53:29.064
And the sacred place was the point
within the center of the circle...

53:29.764 --> 53:32.127
...the origin of all things.

53:34.573 --> 53:37.283
Therefore, should we adore it.

54:07.573 --> 54:09.743
Good morning, Sergeant Griff.

54:09.843 --> 54:12.079
Congratulations on your promotion.

54:12.779 --> 54:15.849
