the way you love Trish.

58:39.462 --> 58:41.329
No one.

58:47.086 --> 58:49.361
What about your husband?

58:49.822 --> 58:51.991
My husband never loved me.

58:52.091 --> 58:55.385
He couldn't wait to get away from me.

58:55.761 --> 58:57.569
I'm sorry.

59:06.572 --> 59:11.177
Sometimes I think Trish
would like to get away from me, too.

59:11.677 --> 59:13.264
Poor baby.

59:13.946 --> 59:16.687
Poor, poor baby.

59:45.711 --> 59:47.610
So, tell me...

59:48.382 --> 59:50.450
...what turns you on?

59:52.016 --> 59:54.026
What turns me on?

59:56.304 --> 59:59.439
