01:03:29.568 --> 01:03:31.609
I'm the love witch.

01:03:32.771 --> 01:03:35.515
I'm your ultimate fantasy.

01:03:36.175 --> 01:03:38.049
That's right.

01:03:39.979 --> 01:03:42.052
That's right.

01:03:47.953 --> 01:03:50.156
