01:48:48.285 --> 01:48:51.172
Sometimes it's almost scary
how strong the love gets.

01:48:51.421 --> 01:48:53.061
Love?

01:48:54.122 --> 01:48:56.165
What do you know about love?

01:48:56.593 --> 01:49:00.764
