personality disorder.

01:49:01.564 --> 01:49:03.099
Or worse.

01:49:03.199 --> 01:49:05.074
Don't diagnose me.

01:49:05.718 --> 01:49:08.895
Maybe you're a narcissist who can't love.

01:49:10.206 --> 01:49:12.375
You think that I'm sick...

01:49:12.475 --> 01:49:14.912
...because you've never loved like I have.

01:49:16.012 --> 01:49:19.414
Well, I would do anything for love.

01:49:20.483 --> 01:49:24.452
That's right, you'll never get enough love.

01:49:25.354 --> 01:49:28.492
Even when a man loves you
so much it kills him...

01:49:28.592 --> 01:49:32.396
