01:49:47.610 --> 01:49:49.418
I don't love you.

01:49:55.317 --> 01:49:59.481
How can you stand there and boast
about being immune to love?

01:50:00.023 --> 01:50:04.100
Why does the genuine love
of a woman scare you so much?

01:50:04.728 --> 01:50:08.065
You think that your way
is a superior way to live?

01:50:08.165 --> 01:50:10.767
