01:50:25.748 --> 01:50:28.649
My ex-husband was just like you.

01:50:29.285 --> 01:50:32.462
He used to punish me
by withholding his love from me.

01:50:33.957 --> 01:50:38.361
All my life I've been tossed
in the garbage...

01:50:38.461 --> 01:50:41.889
...except when men wanted to use my body.

01:50:43.165 --> 01:50:46.264
So, I decided to find my own power.

01:50:46.936 --> 01:50:50.013
And I found that power through witchcraft.

01:50:51.540 --> 01:50:54.311
That means that I take
what I need from men...

01:50:54.411 --> 01:50:56.688
...and not the other way around.

01:50:59.615 --> 01:51:01.690
I'm sorry, Elaine.

01:51:03.836 --> 01:51:05.845
It won't work this time.

01:51:06.989 --> 01:51:09.759
I'm afraid I'm going to have to arrest you.

01:51:09.859 --> 01:51:11.666
