01:51:26.942 --> 01:51:30.150
No, not burned...

01:51:31.563 --> 01:51:34.948
...but you'll be booked for burying
Wayne Peters illegally.

01:51:36.918 --> 01:51:39.077
And we'll find out more.

01:51:41.589 --> 01:51:43.799
That's the witch who killed the teacher.

01:51:44.860 --> 01:51:47.597
